WEBVTT

00:03.560 --> 00:07.200
<font color="#00ffff">How sharper than a serpent's tooth</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it is to have a thankless child.</font>

00:07.240 --> 00:10.920
<font color="#00ff00">I'm afraid the strain of her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">position has disordered her senses.</font>

00:10.960 --> 00:13.560
How will I manage?

00:13.600 --> 00:15.920
<font color="#ffff00">It does not matter who you like or</font>
<font color="#ffff00">do not like.</font>

00:15.960 --> 00:17.920
Lord Melbourne, you forget yourself.

00:17.960 --> 00:22.080
<font color="#00ffff">I knew I'd seen you before.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">The question is, how you got from</font>
<font color="#00ffff">there to Buck House.</font>

00:22.360 --> 00:23.400
<font color="#00ff00">From </font><font color="#00ff00"> Lord Melbourne.</font>

00:24.320 --> 00:28.400
<font color="#00ffff">So you do know the Queen must marry.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">And she will look to her husband.</font>

00:29.600 --> 00:35.000
# Gloriana

00:36.000 --> 00:41.160
# Hallelujah

