01:48.760 --> 01:50.560
VICTORIA:
My Lords and Gentlemen...

01:51.160 --> 01:55.920
the external tranquillity,
which at present happily prevails...

01:57.200 --> 02:00.800
..make this a fortunate time
in the government of this great
nation.

02:00.840 --> 02:01.920
(Angry shouting)

02:01.960 --> 02:06.560
I pray the blessings of Almighty God
may rest upon your counsel.

02:07.760 --> 02:09.280
(Bugles)

02:09.320 --> 02:11.320
<font color="#ffff00">MILITIA CAPTAIN: Present arms!</font>

02:12.120 --> 02:13.720
<font color="#ffff00">Aim!</font>

02:14.920 --> 02:16.120
(Cries out angrily)

02:16.160 --> 02:18.080
<font color="#ffff00">Come on!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(Shouting)</font>

02:19.840 --> 02:22.360
<font color="#ffff00">In the name of the Queen! Fire!</font>

02:28.000 --> 02:30.360
How was I yesterday, Lord M?

02:30.400 --> 02:32.920
I was trying so hard not to look
at my Uncle Cumberland.

02:32.960 --> 02:35.040
He was glaring at me so ferociously.

02:35.080 --> 02:37.200
I believe he was trying to put me
off.

02:37.240 --> 02:39.240
<font color="#ffff00">It's very likely, Ma'am.</font>

02:40.600 --> 02:42.520
I am plagued by uncles.

02:43.600 --> 02:46.760
My mother's brother Leopold
has written to say he's coming to
visit.

02:46.800 --> 02:49.000
<font color="#ffff00">And how delighted you look at the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">prospect.</font>

02:50.040 --> 02:54.040
He wants to lecture me
on how it is my duty to get married.

02:54.080 --> 02:56.000
<font color="#ffff00">Not all Queens marry, Ma'am.</font>

03:00.320 --> 03:02.320
Do you think she was lonely?

03:04.080 --> 03:08.000
<font color="#ffff00">I believe...she...found companions.</font>

03:09.440 --> 03:12.160
Well, I have no intention of
marrying at present.

03:14.600 --> 03:16.640
I have not seen so many happy
marriages.

03:16.680 --> 03:18.440
<font color="#ffff00">Neither have I, Ma'am.</font>

03:21.440 --> 03:23.200
<font color="#ffff00">Neither have I.</font>

03:25.120 --> 03:28.760
<font color="#00ffff">Excuse me, Majesty,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">there is a messenger asking</font>

03:28.800 --> 03:31.600
<font color="#00ffff">that Lord Melbourne should return</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to the House at once.</font>

03:45.320 --> 03:47.320
(Whispered conversation)

03:51.720 --> 03:54.560
<font color="#00ff00">His Majesty King Leopold!</font>

03:57.480 --> 03:59.680
<font color="#00ffff">Welcome to Buckingham Palace,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Uncle Leopold.</font>

04:02.600 --> 04:06.120
<font color="#ffff00">How fortunate that you have</font>
<font color="#ffff00">inherited your excellent posture</font>

04:06.160 --> 04:08.480
<font color="#ffff00">from our side of the family,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria.</font>

04:08.520 --> 04:11.840
<font color="#ffff00">It quite makes up for your lack of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">inches.</font>

04:13.320 --> 04:18.040
<font color="#ffff00">Just think if my poor dear Charlotte</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and our child had survived,</font>

04:18.079 --> 04:21.399
<font color="#ffff00">I would be living in these gilded</font>
<font color="#ffff00">halls...</font>

04:22.480 --> 04:27.320
<font color="#ffff00">..and you, no doubt, would be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">leading a blameless life in Coburg.</font>

04:31.440 --> 04:33.600
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, sister.</font>

04:34.040 --> 04:35.760
<font color="#00ffff">Dear brother.</font>

04:35.800 --> 04:37.280
<font color="#00ffff">I am so happy to see you.</font>

04:37.320 --> 04:39.840
<font color="#00ffff">You must talk to Victoria about</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Albert.</font>

04:39.880 --> 04:42.680
Why should Uncle Leopold
talk to me about Albert, Mama?

04:42.720 --> 04:44.320
Has he had an accident?

04:44.360 --> 04:50.840
<font color="#ffff00">On the contrary, Albert has finished</font>
<font color="#ffff00">his studies and is the most</font>
<font color="#ffff00">admirable young man.</font>

04:50.880 --> 04:53.880
<font color="#ffff00">You could not hope for a better</font>
<font color="#ffff00">husband, than my nephew.</font>

04:53.920 --> 04:56.440
Then he must have changed
since the last time I saw him.

04:56.480 --> 04:59.800
He didn't smile, he didn't dance
and he fell asleep at half-past nine.

05:00.480 --> 05:03.120
<font color="#ffff00">You will exaggerate like all young</font>
<font color="#ffff00">girls.</font>

05:03.160 --> 05:08.160
<font color="#ffff00">That is why you need wiser heads</font>
<font color="#ffff00">around you to preserve you from your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">own folly.</font>

05:08.200 --> 05:09.840
I think I manage quite well.

05:09.880 --> 05:14.520
<font color="#ffff00">Of course, you have the excellent</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and devoted Lord Melbourne.</font>

05:15.560 --> 05:17.960
<font color="#ffff00">But he will not be at your side</font>
<font color="#ffff00">forever.</font>

05:18.000 --> 05:19.400
<font color="#00ff00">No, he will not.</font>

05:19.440 --> 05:21.760
<font color="#00ff00">You need a husband to advise you.</font>

05:23.480 --> 05:27.440
Oh, well, unless you have something
else to tell me that I don't know,
you must excuse me.

05:27.480 --> 05:29.960
I have Government business to attend
to.

05:30.000 --> 05:32.680
But I'm sure Mama
has a great deal to say to you.

05:36.160 --> 05:40.240
<font color="#00ff00">Five years ago, he was just</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a German Princeling and now he's...</font>

05:40.280 --> 05:43.520
<font color="#00ff00">Leopold, King of the Belgians,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">indeed.</font>

05:44.080 --> 05:48.840
<font color="#00ff00">He's here to fix a match</font>
<font color="#00ff00">between Victoria and that stripling,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Albert.</font>

05:50.560 --> 05:54.440
<font color="#00ff00">He means to put a Coburg</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on every throne in Europe.</font>

05:55.560 --> 05:59.480
<font color="#00ffff">Then I suggest that you promote your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">nephew.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">George Cambridge?</font>

06:00.840 --> 06:03.240
<font color="#00ff00">You may be right. Keep it in the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">family.</font>

06:04.440 --> 06:07.920
<font color="#ffff00">I remember Leopold being most</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ambitious for the Coburgs.</font>

06:07.960 --> 06:09.840
Nothing has changed.

06:09.880 --> 06:12.280
He has a plan to marry me to my
cousin Albert.

06:13.080 --> 06:16.080
<font color="#ffff00">I do not think marriage</font>
<font color="#ffff00">between first cousins is wise,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am.</font>

06:16.760 --> 06:18.720
There is no need to look so worried,
Lord M.

06:19.520 --> 06:21.480
I told him it would never do.

06:21.520 --> 06:25.080
<font color="#ffff00">If I seem concerned,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it is not on account of your Uncle</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Leopold.</font>

06:25.760 --> 06:30.640
<font color="#ffff00">I fear there has been an uprising in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Wales by a group calling themselves</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Chartists.</font>

06:30.680 --> 06:32.080
What a strange name.

06:32.120 --> 06:36.920
<font color="#ffff00">So called because they've written a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">charter demanding universal</font>
<font color="#ffff00">suffrage, annual elections,</font>

06:36.960 --> 06:39.440
<font color="#ffff00">a secret ballot and even payment for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">MPs.</font>

06:39.480 --> 06:43.520
<font color="#ffff00">Their ideas are impossible, of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">course, but they have much support</font>
<font color="#ffff00">among a certain class.</font>

06:43.560 --> 06:47.160
You tell me the British are not
revolutionary.
<font color="#ffff00">I don't believe they are.</font>

06:47.200 --> 06:51.560
<font color="#ffff00">But this year's harvest failed, and</font>
<font color="#ffff00">when people are hungry they fancy</font>
<font color="#ffff00">themselves radicals.</font>

06:51.600 --> 06:55.200
<font color="#ffff00">You and your safety are the only</font>
<font color="#ffff00">things that disturb my peace of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">mind.</font>

06:56.320 --> 06:59.400
And you will you come with me,
to the opera tonight?

06:59.440 --> 07:02.480
I do not think I can bear an evening
alone with Uncle Leopold.

07:03.240 --> 07:06.280
<font color="#ffff00">You forget the Russian Grand Duke</font>
<font color="#ffff00">will also be there.</font>

07:06.320 --> 07:09.320
<font color="#ffff00">You seemed to enjoy his company</font>
<font color="#ffff00">very much at the Coronation Ball.</font>

07:09.360 --> 07:12.480
He dances well enough
but he is no substitute for you, Lord
M.

07:12.520 --> 07:16.720
<font color="#ffff00">You flatter me, Ma'am,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and like all men I am susceptible to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">flattery.</font>

07:19.800 --> 07:24.200
# Il dolce suono...Spargi d'amaro
pianto

07:50.400 --> 07:54.160
(# Prolonged final note)

08:00.160 --> 08:02.160
(Cheering and applause)

08:04.200 --> 08:06.520
The "Mad Scene" always makes me cry.

08:06.560 --> 08:09.320
<font color="#00ffff">I think that is the point of opera.</font>

08:10.680 --> 08:13.840
<font color="#00ffff">We do not have so many opportunities</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to cry, you and I.</font>

08:15.840 --> 08:17.360
How true.

08:17.400 --> 08:22.800
<font color="#00ff00">George, you should go to the royal</font>
<font color="#00ff00">box now before she sits on that</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Russian's lap.</font>

08:23.800 --> 08:26.520
<font color="#00ffff">So long as I don't have to stay</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for the second act.</font>

08:26.560 --> 08:28.680
<font color="#00ffff">I've heard better singing in the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">mess.</font>

08:30.720 --> 08:33.799
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I hear Prince Albert</font>
<font color="#ffff00">is a most correct young man.</font>

08:33.840 --> 08:38.640
<font color="#00ffff">Exactly. What we need is an English</font>
<font color="#00ffff">bridegroom like Prince George.</font>

08:38.679 --> 08:41.400
<font color="#00ff00">I thought she still likes the Grand</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Duke.</font>

08:41.440 --> 08:43.360
<font color="#00ff00">Such a handsome young man.</font>

08:43.400 --> 08:45.600
<font color="#00ffff">And what do you think, Miss</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Skerrett?</font>

08:45.640 --> 08:49.920
<font color="#00ffff">You are very quiet, but er... I</font>
<font color="#00ffff">suspect you're an expert in matters</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of the heart.</font>

08:49.960 --> 08:53.280
<font color="#ffff00">Seems to me the only man</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the Queen really likes is Lord</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Melbourne.</font>

08:53.320 --> 08:55.520
<font color="#00ff00">I think we should have a wager.</font>

08:58.680 --> 09:01.160
<font color="#00ff00">The Rooshian for Mrs Jenkins...</font>

09:02.480 --> 09:07.320
<font color="#00ff00">..the German sausage for Mr</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Francatelli, I'll take the English</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Bulldog.</font>

09:07.360 --> 09:09.080
<font color="#00ff00">Sixpence each.</font>

09:09.120 --> 09:11.800
<font color="#00ff00">Will you join us, Miss Skerrett? No?</font>

09:12.560 --> 09:14.560
<font color="#00ff00">How about you, Brodie?</font>

09:14.960 --> 09:16.760
<font color="#00ffff">I don't have a sixpence, Mr Penge.</font>

09:18.720 --> 09:20.200
<font color="#00ffff">I wish I had.</font>

09:21.440 --> 09:25.200
I believe you have met my cousin,
Prince George of Cambridge.

09:27.280 --> 09:29.640
<font color="#00ff00">I have had the honour to inspect his</font>
<font color="#00ff00">regiments.</font>

09:29.680 --> 09:33.080
<font color="#00ff00">Such fine uniforms.</font>

09:34.280 --> 09:36.000
<font color="#ffff00">You're very kind, Sir.</font>

09:37.760 --> 09:41.600
What did you think of the "Mad
Scene", George? Did it bring tears to
your eyes?

09:41.640 --> 09:43.640
<font color="#ffff00">It certainly did.</font>

09:47.320 --> 09:49.320
# D'immenso giubilo

09:56.000 --> 09:58.400
(Chorus start singing)

10:14.280 --> 10:15.880
<font color="#ffff00">LEOPOLD: My dear niece...</font>

10:16.760 --> 10:19.960
<font color="#ffff00">..you know I have always tried to be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a father to you.</font>

10:20.000 --> 10:23.480
You have certainly written to me
often enough. Hasn't he, Dash?

10:24.120 --> 10:26.360
<font color="#ffff00">Please talk to me and not to your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">lapdog.</font>

10:26.400 --> 10:28.680
<font color="#ffff00">I have something important to say to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you.</font>

10:28.720 --> 10:30.160
And we are listening.

10:31.880 --> 10:34.800
<font color="#ffff00">You say you do not want to marry</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Albert,</font>

10:34.840 --> 10:38.760
<font color="#ffff00">but I would ask you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if you intend to marry someone else?</font>

10:38.800 --> 10:40.840
<font color="#ffff00">I have no plans to marry anyone at</font>
<font color="#ffff00">present.</font>

10:41.280 --> 10:43.720
<font color="#ffff00">You do not, I hope, imagine...</font>

10:43.760 --> 10:48.440
<font color="#ffff00">that your Lord M could ever be more</font>
<font color="#ffff00">than your Prime Minister?</font>

10:48.480 --> 10:51.120
I will not dignify that suggestion
with an answer.

10:51.160 --> 10:55.520
<font color="#ffff00">Then as one sovereign to another,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I would advise you to be careful.</font>

10:56.040 --> 11:00.480
I think you forget that I am of a
royal line that stretches back a
thousand years...

11:01.120 --> 11:05.440
..whereas you are King of Belgium -
a country that did not exist a decade
ago.

11:06.520 --> 11:09.760
<font color="#ffff00">Even the British Crown is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">vulnerable.</font>

11:11.480 --> 11:15.440
<font color="#ffff00">Only this week</font>
<font color="#ffff00">there was an armed uprising in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Newport.</font>

11:15.480 --> 11:19.160
<font color="#ffff00">Who knows where these Chartists</font>
<font color="#ffff00">will strike next?</font>

11:19.800 --> 11:23.240
<font color="#ffff00">You think your monarchy burns</font>
<font color="#ffff00">brightly, Victoria...</font>

11:23.880 --> 11:28.560
<font color="#ffff00">but all it takes is a little draught</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from the wrong direction.</font>

11:29.320 --> 11:34.640
<font color="#ffff00">Marry Albert and start a family</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your subjects can be proud of...</font>

11:35.600 --> 11:37.280
<font color="#ffff00">..otherwise...</font>

11:53.680 --> 11:56.520
<font color="#00ff00">From your sister in Monmouth, Mrs</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Jenkins.</font>

11:57.280 --> 11:59.720
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, and you owe me a shilling for</font>
<font color="#00ff00">postage.</font>

12:12.680 --> 12:14.680
<font color="#00ffff">Mrs Jenkins, are you all right?</font>

12:18.080 --> 12:20.080
<font color="#00ffff">Mrs Jenkins?</font>

12:32.120 --> 12:34.120
Did you enjoy Lucia last night?

12:36.600 --> 12:38.320
<font color="#ffff00">It's not Mozart, Ma'am.</font>

12:38.360 --> 12:39.600
And you?

12:39.640 --> 12:41.240
<font color="#ffff00">You seemed well attended.</font>

12:41.280 --> 12:42.800
The Grand Duke is amusing.

12:42.840 --> 12:46.960
It is refreshing to have someone who
understands the cares of my position.

12:47.000 --> 12:49.560
But he's too foreign to be entirely
comfortable.

12:50.120 --> 12:52.440
<font color="#ffff00">And Prince George?</font>

12:52.480 --> 12:54.680
He is so pleased with himself.
<font color="#ffff00">Oh? Well...</font>

12:54.720 --> 12:59.760
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps...but I think he would like</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to be a candidate for your hand.</font>

12:59.800 --> 13:02.560
<font color="#ffff00">An English marriage would be very</font>
<font color="#ffff00">popular.</font>

13:03.000 --> 13:05.320
An English marriage?

13:06.480 --> 13:08.480
<font color="#ffff00">Would go down very well.</font>

13:12.720 --> 13:14.720
I shall bear that in mind, Lord M.

13:17.320 --> 13:20.080
<font color="#00ff00">I hope, Sir, you can persuade the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Queen</font>

13:20.120 --> 13:23.400
<font color="#00ff00">of the benefits of a match</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with your nephew Albert.</font>

13:24.240 --> 13:29.240
<font color="#ffff00">There are some...</font>
<font color="#ffff00">obstacles that need to be removed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">first.</font>

13:29.280 --> 13:31.000
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, indeed, Sir.</font>

13:32.200 --> 13:33.560
<font color="#00ffff">Good morning, Leopold.</font>

13:36.880 --> 13:39.160
<font color="#00ffff">Sir John.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Ma'am.</font>

13:39.200 --> 13:42.080
<font color="#00ff00">If you will excuse me,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I have some matters to attend to.</font>

13:42.120 --> 13:43.840
<font color="#00ffff">But you will be here later?</font>

13:43.880 --> 13:46.080
<font color="#00ffff">For the ceremony?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Yes. Of course.</font>

13:50.200 --> 13:53.720
<font color="#00ffff">I was hoping, Leopold,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you might lend me some money.</font>

13:54.440 --> 13:57.440
<font color="#00ffff">As you see, I am living like a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">pauper.</font>

13:57.480 --> 14:03.640
<font color="#00ff00">Well, I would love to, but Belgium</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is such a poor little country, not</font>
<font color="#00ff00">like Britain.</font>

14:04.640 --> 14:08.320
<font color="#ffff00">I wonder if Victoria might not be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a little more generous</font>

14:08.360 --> 14:11.480
<font color="#ffff00">if you were to make some changes</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to your household.</font>

14:11.520 --> 14:15.680
<font color="#ffff00">She does not care,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I think, for the admirable Conroy.</font>

14:15.720 --> 14:17.720
<font color="#00ffff">He's my friend.</font>

14:18.520 --> 14:20.680
<font color="#00ffff">I cannot live without him.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps.</font>

14:21.080 --> 14:25.200
<font color="#ffff00">But, my dear sister,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I wonder if Sir John feels the same?</font>

14:33.760 --> 14:35.600
<font color="#00ff00">Mrs Jenkins?</font>

14:37.000 --> 14:39.560
<font color="#00ff00">The Baroness needs the keys</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to the orders cupboard.</font>

14:39.600 --> 14:41.960
<font color="#00ff00">I said you were ill,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but she sent me to fetch them.</font>

14:43.280 --> 14:45.280
(Keys jangle)

14:52.640 --> 14:54.400
(Gulls cry)

14:54.440 --> 14:56.440
Why are there so many soldiers, Lord
M?

14:56.480 --> 15:00.520
<font color="#ffff00">I'm afraid there may be some</font>
<font color="#ffff00">disturbance from the Chartists,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am.</font>

15:00.560 --> 15:03.760
<font color="#ffff00">Since Newport,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the movement has grown in strength.</font>

15:05.760 --> 15:08.000
Do Chartists wear bonnets?

15:08.040 --> 15:10.960
Because there are a great many of
them out there today.

15:11.000 --> 15:14.240
<font color="#ffff00">Some Chartists do believe that women</font>
<font color="#ffff00">should have the vote, Ma'am.</font>

15:15.000 --> 15:17.000
Now you are teasing me.

15:19.680 --> 15:23.320
<font color="#00ffff">We are fortunate, Sir, that your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">father the Emperor can spare you for</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the opening</font>

15:23.360 --> 15:25.000
<font color="#00ffff">of a monument to the Duke of Kent.</font>

15:26.040 --> 15:31.640
<font color="#00ff00">My father and I are great admirers</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of British institutions, your Queen</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in particular.</font>

15:39.040 --> 15:44.200
I never knew my father,
but I know he would have been
delighted

15:44.240 --> 15:46.640
to have his charitable endeavours
commemorated

15:46.680 --> 15:48.960
by the most generous people of this
town.

15:49.440 --> 15:53.440
So it gives me great pleasure
to dedicate this to his memory.

15:59.520 --> 16:01.840
Thank you so much, but I believe I
can manage.

16:11.440 --> 16:15.160
<font color="#00ffff">Freedom for the Newport Chartists!</font>

16:15.200 --> 16:17.200
(Crowd yells)

16:17.680 --> 16:19.600
<font color="#00ffff">Freedom for the Chartists!</font>

16:19.640 --> 16:23.280
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Alfred, I believe the Queen is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">leaving. Will you escort her and the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Duchess?</font>

16:23.320 --> 16:25.320
<font color="#00ffff">With pleasure.</font>

16:32.440 --> 16:34.800
<font color="#00ff00">Lord Melbourne, may I have a word?</font>

16:34.840 --> 16:36.640
<font color="#ffff00">Can it wait?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I think not.</font>

16:36.680 --> 16:38.680
<font color="#00ff00">I wish to talk to you about my</font>
<font color="#00ff00">niece.</font>

16:40.400 --> 16:42.040
<font color="#ffff00">Indeed?</font>

16:42.080 --> 16:45.320
<font color="#00ff00">You must admit, I think,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that the sooner she is married the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">better.</font>

16:45.360 --> 16:47.720
<font color="#00ff00">Her reign so far has been troubled.</font>

16:48.720 --> 16:52.960
<font color="#00ff00">A husband, children,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">could steady her giddiness...</font>

16:53.840 --> 16:56.080
<font color="#ffff00">I do not see the urgency for her to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">marry.</font>

16:56.760 --> 16:59.720
<font color="#ffff00">It is more important, I think,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that she chooses wisely.</font>

16:59.760 --> 17:02.920
<font color="#00ff00">There could be no better choice</font>
<font color="#00ff00">than her cousin Albert.</font>

17:02.960 --> 17:09.160
<font color="#00ff00">He takes after me in so many ways</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and he is, of course, the same age</font>
<font color="#00ff00">as her.</font>

17:11.480 --> 17:14.720
<font color="#ffff00">I do not believe she took to him</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the last time they met.</font>

17:14.760 --> 17:16.760
<font color="#00ff00">Victoria will change her mind,</font>

17:16.800 --> 17:21.640
<font color="#00ff00">but only, I think, if she</font>
<font color="#00ff00">understands that such a marriage is</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in her best interest.</font>

17:21.680 --> 17:26.400
<font color="#00ff00">I believe, my Lord,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you could persuade her of that.</font>

17:26.440 --> 17:29.000
<font color="#ffff00">I think you exaggerate my influence,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Sir.</font>

17:29.040 --> 17:32.280
<font color="#00ff00">I have seen the way my niece looks</font>
<font color="#00ff00">at you.</font>

17:44.760 --> 17:46.760
(Sighs)

18:11.240 --> 18:14.640
<font color="#00ffff">Ah, the complicated Miss Skerrett.</font>

18:14.680 --> 18:17.200
<font color="#00ffff">Are you now a...er...laundry maid</font>
<font color="#00ffff">as well as a dresser?</font>

18:17.240 --> 18:20.920
<font color="#00ff00">The laundry maid has sprained her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">ankle, so I thought I'd take these</font>
<font color="#00ff00">down myself.</font>

18:21.440 --> 18:23.720
<font color="#00ffff">When are you going to smile on me,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Miss Skerrett?</font>

18:23.760 --> 18:27.040
<font color="#00ffff">If you come down to the kitchen,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I've made some sweet meats, just for</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you.</font>

18:27.080 --> 18:31.920
<font color="#00ffff">You know, I used to send them, to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the nunnery. I believe they were</font>
<font color="#00ffff">much appreciated there.</font>

18:31.960 --> 18:34.680
<font color="#00ff00">But I do not have a sweet tooth, Mr</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Francatelli.</font>

18:34.720 --> 18:38.160
<font color="#00ff00">Whatever I was before I came here</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is my own business.</font>

18:41.120 --> 18:43.560
<font color="#00ffff">I trust you've recovered from</font>
<font color="#00ffff">yesterday, Ma'am.</font>

18:43.600 --> 18:45.760
<font color="#00ffff">The impudence of the Chartists.</font>

18:45.800 --> 18:49.160
I thought they looked hungry
rather than dangerous.

18:56.680 --> 19:00.760
Where is Lord M?
I thought he should be here by now.

19:04.840 --> 19:07.920
Is he indisposed?
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, no, Ma'am, he's quite well.</font>

19:07.960 --> 19:11.480
Then why isn't he here?
<font color="#00ffff">He has gone to Brocket Hall.</font>

19:15.200 --> 19:17.560
Emma, your carriage is unmarked, I
believe.

19:53.280 --> 19:56.080
<font color="#ffff00">Ah, it is you, Ma'am. I couldn't</font>
<font color="#ffff00">tell.</font>

19:57.560 --> 20:00.960
The butler said you would be here.
<font color="#ffff00">I come here for the rooks.</font>

20:01.000 --> 20:03.000
<font color="#ffff00">They're sociable animals.</font>

20:04.360 --> 20:06.880
<font color="#ffff00">A gathering like this is called a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">parliament.</font>

20:08.280 --> 20:11.600
<font color="#ffff00">Altogether more civilised</font>
<font color="#ffff00">than their human equivalent.</font>

20:16.080 --> 20:18.080
I'm sorry to disturb you, Lord M...

20:20.600 --> 20:22.120
..but I had to talk to you.

20:22.160 --> 20:24.440
<font color="#ffff00">Brocket Hall is honoured, Ma'am.</font>

20:24.480 --> 20:27.360
I have come here incognito, of
course.
<font color="#ffff00">Of course.</font>

20:27.400 --> 20:30.120
<font color="#ffff00">But your presence cannot be entirely</font>
<font color="#ffff00">disguised.</font>

20:38.880 --> 20:41.080
Yesterday I realised something.

20:44.000 --> 20:46.000
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, Ma'am?</font>

20:49.680 --> 20:52.200
I think perhaps now...

20:52.240 --> 20:56.000
I'm speaking as a woman and not as a
queen.

21:01.320 --> 21:04.000
At the beginning...

21:05.040 --> 21:07.600
..I thought that you
were the father I never had.

21:09.440 --> 21:12.640
But now I feel, I know...

21:16.440 --> 21:19.520
..that you are the only companion
I could ever desire.

21:32.880 --> 21:34.880
<font color="#ffff00">Did you know that...</font>

21:35.600 --> 21:38.080
<font color="#ffff00">..that rooks mate for life?</font>

21:40.480 --> 21:44.520
<font color="#ffff00">Every year, they...</font>
<font color="#ffff00">they build their nests together...</font>

21:46.960 --> 21:51.640
<font color="#ffff00">..renew all those little civilities</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that...</font>

21:53.040 --> 21:55.040
<font color="#ffff00">..make a marriage sparkle.</font>

21:57.080 --> 22:01.160
<font color="#ffff00">I think we could learn much from</font>
<font color="#ffff00">them.</font>

22:02.840 --> 22:06.760
<font color="#ffff00">If I had just spent more time</font>
<font color="#ffff00">watching the rooks...</font>

22:08.440 --> 22:10.520
<font color="#ffff00">..my wife would have felt more</font>
<font color="#ffff00">attended to.</font>

22:10.560 --> 22:12.560
She should never have left you.

22:14.000 --> 22:16.000
I would never do such a thing.

22:17.400 --> 22:18.520
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

22:21.080 --> 22:24.720
<font color="#ffff00">I believe when you give your heart</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it will be without hesitation.</font>

22:26.760 --> 22:28.760
<font color="#ffff00">But you cannot give it to me.</font>

22:31.760 --> 22:33.960
I think you have it already.

22:35.400 --> 22:38.120
<font color="#ffff00">No, you must keep it intact for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">someone else.</font>

22:40.360 --> 22:42.360
<font color="#ffff00">For I have no use for it, you see.</font>

22:45.160 --> 22:48.840
<font color="#ffff00">Like a rook, I mate for life.</font>

22:52.560 --> 22:54.560
I see.

23:00.480 --> 23:03.560
Then I am sorry to have disturbed
you, Lord Melbourne.

23:37.000 --> 23:43.080
<font color="#00ffff">Ah, Baroness, are you standing guard</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in case your charge disappears</font>
<font color="#00ffff">again?</font>

23:43.120 --> 23:45.480
<font color="#00ffff">I hear she went to Brocket Hall</font>
<font color="#00ffff">without an escort.</font>

23:45.920 --> 23:49.400
<font color="#00ff00">I am no longer the Queen's</font>
<font color="#00ff00">governess, Sir John.</font>

23:49.440 --> 23:51.920
<font color="#00ffff">Or her confidante, it seems.</font>

23:51.960 --> 23:55.280
<font color="#00ffff">We are but the playthings of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">princes, Baroness.</font>

23:55.320 --> 23:59.600
<font color="#00ffff">You see, I had such hopes,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of bringing some rigour to the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">monarchy.</font>

24:00.840 --> 24:04.400
<font color="#00ffff">But Queen Victoria has been allowed</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to squander the good will of the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">country</font>

24:04.440 --> 24:08.680
<font color="#00ffff">in a series of the most squalid</font>
<font color="#00ffff">episodes.</font>

24:08.720 --> 24:13.920
<font color="#00ff00">You have no right</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to speak about the Queen in such a</font>
<font color="#00ff00">way.</font>

24:16.560 --> 24:18.040
<font color="#00ffff">No right?</font>

24:18.080 --> 24:21.800
<font color="#00ffff">The only hope now is that she</font>
<font color="#00ffff">marries a man who can control her.</font>

24:30.560 --> 24:34.160
<font color="#ffff00">Where have you been, Drina?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">No-one could tell me where you were.</font>

24:35.520 --> 24:37.000
It doesn't matter, Mama.

24:37.040 --> 24:40.760
<font color="#00ff00">Wherever you have been,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">it seems it did not make you happy.</font>

24:41.400 --> 24:46.640
<font color="#00ff00">Perhaps now you will be in a more</font>
<font color="#00ff00">receptive frame of mind to discuss</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Albert's visit.</font>

24:46.680 --> 24:52.920
<font color="#00ff00">No? I must attend to my costume for</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the ball you are so kindly holding</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for me.</font>

24:55.000 --> 24:59.280
<font color="#ffff00">Please invite dear Albert to visit.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">He would be such a good companion</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for you.</font>

24:59.320 --> 25:02.640
I don't want a stupid boy like
Albert, Mama. Or anyone else.

25:11.600 --> 25:13.600
(Knocks on door)

25:13.640 --> 25:16.000
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps you would like one of these,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Miss Skerrett?</font>

25:16.040 --> 25:18.840
<font color="#00ff00">No, thank you.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I told you I don't have a sweet</font>
<font color="#00ff00">tooth.</font>

25:18.880 --> 25:23.120
<font color="#00ffff">That's funny. The other girls at Ma</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Fletcher's couldn't get enough of my</font>
<font color="#00ffff">strawberry tarts.</font>

25:24.200 --> 25:26.200
<font color="#00ff00">I wouldn't know.</font>

25:28.960 --> 25:31.480
<font color="#00ff00">I wasn't an upstairs girl. I worked</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in the laundry.</font>

25:33.520 --> 25:35.520
<font color="#00ffff">It's quite a jump...</font>

25:36.320 --> 25:40.080
<font color="#00ffff">..going from cleaning up after tarts</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to mending the Queen's stockings.</font>

25:41.760 --> 25:44.720
<font color="#00ffff">I can't for the life of me figure</font>
<font color="#00ffff">out how you did it.</font>

25:44.760 --> 25:46.880
<font color="#00ffff">It's a veritable mystery.</font>

25:47.600 --> 25:50.640
<font color="#00ff00">I don't know what you want,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but you ain't getting nothing from</font>
<font color="#00ff00">me.</font>

25:50.680 --> 25:53.400
<font color="#00ffff">All I want is for us to be friends.</font>

25:54.880 --> 25:57.280
<font color="#00ffff">I had to work hard to get here, just</font>
<font color="#00ffff">like you.</font>

25:59.000 --> 26:01.000
<font color="#00ffff">I think we might be kindred spirits.</font>

26:01.840 --> 26:06.920
<font color="#00ff00">I don't have friends, Mr</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Francatelli, or kindred spirits</font>
<font color="#00ff00">neither.</font>

26:19.000 --> 26:20.800
(Horse whinnies)

26:25.840 --> 26:27.840
<font color="#00ffff">How splendid you look, Ma'am.</font>

26:30.320 --> 26:32.320
Do you really think so?

26:33.600 --> 26:35.600
<font color="#00ffff">What beautiful flowers.</font>

26:36.560 --> 26:38.600
<font color="#00ffff">They're orchids.</font>

26:38.640 --> 26:40.840
<font color="#00ffff">Where did they come from?</font>

26:42.280 --> 26:44.600
Brocket Hall.

26:44.640 --> 26:48.240
<font color="#00ffff">But I thought William had closed</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the greenhouses after Caro...</font>

26:48.840 --> 26:52.640
<font color="#00ffff">He must have opened them again for</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you. </font><font color="#ffffff"> I do not think he would do</font>
anything for me.

26:54.200 --> 26:58.360
<font color="#00ffff">Do you know how hard it is to grow</font>
<font color="#00ffff">orchids? You misjudge him, Ma'am.</font>

26:59.040 --> 27:01.440
He cares only for the memory of his
wife.

27:01.480 --> 27:03.240
<font color="#00ffff">Is that what he told you?</font>

27:03.280 --> 27:06.160
<font color="#00ffff">Then that is what he wants you to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">believe.</font>

27:07.320 --> 27:10.160
<font color="#00ffff">These flowers, Ma'am... Well...</font>

27:29.560 --> 27:32.320
<font color="#00ff00">Carpe diem, George. You must be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">attentive.</font>

27:32.880 --> 27:35.440
<font color="#ffff00">I will stick to her like glue,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for all the good it will do.</font>

27:35.480 --> 27:38.240
<font color="#ffff00">She's the one that has to make the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">running.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Nonsense.</font>

27:38.280 --> 27:41.160
<font color="#00ff00">She's a nineteen-year-old girl.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">You are Sir Galahad.</font>

27:42.160 --> 27:44.160
<font color="#ffff00">Sir Lancelot, actually.</font>

27:44.840 --> 27:47.560
<font color="#00ffff">PENGE: My lords, ladies and</font>
<font color="#00ffff">gentlemen...</font>

27:48.040 --> 27:53.320
<font color="#00ffff">Her Majesty the Queen</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and His Majesty King Leopold of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Belgium.</font>

27:57.520 --> 28:00.760
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty! May I claim the first</font>
<font color="#ffff00">dance?</font>

28:00.800 --> 28:02.960
<font color="#00ff00">May a Cossack dance with the Queen?</font>

28:03.000 --> 28:06.600
I understand Cossacks
can be dangerous if thwarted,

28:07.040 --> 28:10.000
so I shall dance with you first
and you next, Sir Galahad.

28:10.040 --> 28:12.600
<font color="#ffff00">It's Lancelot, actually.</font>

28:12.640 --> 28:15.040
# JOSEF STRAUSS:
Rudolfsheimer-Polka Opus 152

28:24.000 --> 28:26.480
<font color="#00ffff">I hope the Queen has saved a dance</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for you.</font>

28:27.440 --> 28:29.640
<font color="#ffff00">She's busy tonight.</font>

28:33.200 --> 28:35.760
<font color="#00ffff">She will have to marry one day,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">William.</font>

28:35.800 --> 28:37.480
<font color="#ffff00">Yes. She will.</font>

28:37.520 --> 28:40.360
<font color="#ffff00">I just hope her husband will</font>
<font color="#ffff00">appreciate her.</font>

28:51.840 --> 28:54.840
<font color="#00ff00">I took the liberty of bringing you a</font>
<font color="#00ff00">little brandy, Mrs Jenkins.</font>

28:54.880 --> 28:56.880
<font color="#00ff00">Thought you might need it.</font>

28:58.120 --> 29:00.120
<font color="#00ffff">Thank you.</font>

29:02.280 --> 29:04.920
<font color="#00ffff">I have to talk to someone.</font>

29:06.040 --> 29:08.040
<font color="#00ffff">Might as well be you.</font>

29:10.040 --> 29:12.040
<font color="#00ffff">I know you can keep a secret.</font>

29:13.840 --> 29:15.840
<font color="#00ffff">I have a nephew.</font>

29:15.880 --> 29:17.640
<font color="#00ffff">My sister's son.</font>

29:17.680 --> 29:19.680
<font color="#00ffff">He's my godson too.</font>

29:19.720 --> 29:22.760
<font color="#00ffff">Last time I saw him he had blond</font>
<font color="#00ffff">curls all over his head.</font>

29:25.360 --> 29:28.080
<font color="#00ffff">I always thought I'd see him again,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but...</font>

29:28.120 --> 29:31.760
<font color="#00ffff">working for the Household, it made</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it very difficult for me to go back,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you know.</font>

29:31.800 --> 29:35.240
<font color="#00ffff">He would write to me sometimes and</font>
<font color="#00ffff">say that he would come and visit me</font>
<font color="#00ffff">one day.</font>

29:36.720 --> 29:38.720
<font color="#00ffff">And now he's coming to London...</font>

29:41.120 --> 29:46.280
<font color="#00ffff">..to be hanged and then to be cut</font>
<font color="#00ffff">open while he's still alive.</font>

29:47.280 --> 29:51.120
<font color="#00ff00">He's one of the Newport Chartists?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Please. Please.</font>

29:51.680 --> 29:54.080
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, Mrs Jenkins, I am so sorry.</font>

29:54.120 --> 29:57.080
<font color="#00ffff">Don't be. He is a reckless fool</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and he deserves to be punished.</font>

30:02.080 --> 30:04.080
<font color="#00ffff">(Sobs) But not like this.</font>

30:04.120 --> 30:06.120
(Polka ends, applause)

30:09.720 --> 30:11.720
<font color="#00ff00">The Queen is waiting.</font>

30:11.760 --> 30:13.680
<font color="#ffff00">Then why don't you go and dance with</font>
<font color="#ffff00">her?</font>

30:13.720 --> 30:15.880
<font color="#ffff00">I have had quite enough of cousin</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria.</font>

30:15.920 --> 30:18.320
<font color="#ffff00">Why, her legs are shorter than my</font>
<font color="#ffff00">arms.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Imbecile.</font>

30:18.360 --> 30:21.640
<font color="#00ff00">Don't you want to be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the most important man in the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">country?</font>

30:21.680 --> 30:25.160
<font color="#ffff00">I might be the midget's husband,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but I would not be master in my own</font>
<font color="#ffff00">house.</font>

30:25.200 --> 30:27.200
<font color="#ffff00">No, thank you.</font>

30:35.520 --> 30:37.520
<font color="#ffff00">May I have the pleasure, Ma'am?</font>

30:44.000 --> 30:46.000
I think this one is free.

30:53.640 --> 30:55.440
<font color="#ffff00">Have you danced with George yet?</font>

30:56.640 --> 30:58.960
He wants to dance with a queen...

30:59.760 --> 31:01.360
..not necessarily with me.

31:01.400 --> 31:03.960
<font color="#ffff00">Then he's more of a fool, than I</font>
<font color="#ffff00">suspected.</font>

31:05.520 --> 31:07.800
I wasn't sure if I would dance with
you tonight.

31:09.680 --> 31:13.120
<font color="#ffff00">It would be unkind for Elizabeth</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to refuse her Leicester.</font>

31:15.240 --> 31:17.240
Leicester was her companion?

31:17.280 --> 31:19.200
<font color="#ffff00">He was.</font>

31:19.240 --> 31:23.480
<font color="#ffff00">He did have a wife, but then she</font>
<font color="#ffff00">died.</font>

31:24.160 --> 31:28.120
But even though he was free,
they never married.

31:29.280 --> 31:33.240
<font color="#ffff00">I think both he and the Queen</font>
<font color="#ffff00">understood they were not in a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">position to marry.</font>

31:35.080 --> 31:37.080
<font color="#ffff00">Whatever their inclination.</font>

32:00.440 --> 32:02.920
<font color="#00ff00">I am honoured</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that you would dance with me, Ma'am.</font>

32:02.960 --> 32:06.040
I thought I should like to
understand what my mother sees in
you.

32:06.080 --> 32:07.720
<font color="#00ff00">Ah.</font>

32:07.760 --> 32:10.080
Well, I believe she values my
company.

32:10.960 --> 32:15.240
<font color="#00ff00">She's long been a widow, and as you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">know, as your mother, she's in no</font>
<font color="#00ff00">position to remarry.</font>

32:15.920 --> 32:17.800
I see.
<font color="#00ff00">Different for you.</font>

32:18.240 --> 32:21.560
<font color="#00ff00">The country needs an heir to the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">throne and you need a husband,</font>

32:21.600 --> 32:23.600
to keep your behaviour in check.

32:24.400 --> 32:28.560
Really, Sir John? And who would
you recommend to keep me under
control?

32:29.800 --> 32:33.840
<font color="#00ff00">Your mother believes that you would</font>
<font color="#00ff00">be happy with your cousin Albert.</font>

32:35.040 --> 32:36.840
And what do you think?

32:36.880 --> 32:40.760
<font color="#00ff00">I think he's a serious young man. He</font>
<font color="#00ff00">understands the duties of a modern</font>
<font color="#00ff00">monarch.</font>

32:41.520 --> 32:43.920
<font color="#00ff00">He will not be swayed by sentiment</font>
<font color="#00ff00">or folly.</font>

32:46.080 --> 32:48.880
And I suppose you imagine
he will need an advisor?

32:49.640 --> 32:52.960
<font color="#00ff00">Ha! Well, who's to say?</font>

32:54.480 --> 32:57.920
At present I have no intention of
marrying, Sir John.

32:57.960 --> 33:01.720
But if I did, it would not be to
anyone who would choose to be advised
by you.

33:03.120 --> 33:07.600
You may have my mother in your
pocket, but you will never, ever have
me.

33:08.880 --> 33:10.520
<font color="#00ff00">I see.</font>

33:17.600 --> 33:21.760
<font color="#00ff00">I believe my niece made an impromptu</font>
<font color="#00ff00">visit to Brocket Hall.</font>

33:22.960 --> 33:24.960
<font color="#ffff00">You are very well informed, Sir.</font>

33:25.760 --> 33:28.160
<font color="#00ff00">It seemed to leave her in low</font>
<font color="#00ff00">spirits.</font>

33:28.200 --> 33:31.240
<font color="#00ff00">Perhaps she did not get what she</font>
<font color="#00ff00">wanted.</font>

33:32.560 --> 33:33.960
<font color="#ffff00">I could not say.</font>

33:35.320 --> 33:38.280
<font color="#00ff00">You should know that I have sent</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for my nephew Albert.</font>

33:38.320 --> 33:40.240
<font color="#ffff00">Without the Queen's permission?</font>

33:40.280 --> 33:42.560
<font color="#00ff00">The sooner he comes the better.</font>

33:42.600 --> 33:46.400
<font color="#00ff00">A young girl's head can be turned so</font>
<font color="#00ff00">easily.</font>

34:25.600 --> 34:27.400
<font color="#00ff00">I have something for you, Your</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Majesty.</font>

34:28.440 --> 34:31.560
<font color="#00ff00">It's a small...token of our</font>
<font color="#00ff00">friendship.</font>

34:32.840 --> 34:35.960
Oh, how beautiful.

34:37.320 --> 34:39.120
V and A.

34:39.159 --> 34:41.320
<font color="#00ff00">Victoria and Alexander.</font>

34:41.360 --> 34:46.040
<font color="#00ff00">It might not be correct perhaps,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but I hope you will forgive me.</font>

34:47.040 --> 34:49.719
<font color="#00ff00">My father has ordered me</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to return to Petersburg.</font>

34:49.760 --> 34:53.120
<font color="#00ff00">He chose a Danish princess.</font>

34:53.159 --> 34:56.960
<font color="#00ff00">I forget her name but he says</font>
<font color="#00ff00">she's very fond of herring.</font>

34:59.320 --> 35:01.560
I am sure she will be charming.

35:03.000 --> 35:05.840
We cannot marry where we please, you
and I.

35:15.960 --> 35:17.960
<font color="#00ffff">Idiot nephew.</font>

35:23.200 --> 35:27.360
<font color="#00ffff">George called at the Palace this</font>
<font color="#00ffff">morning and was refused an audience.</font>

35:27.400 --> 35:32.160
<font color="#00ffff">We might as well go to Hanover.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">But you are still the heir to the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">throne.</font>

35:32.760 --> 35:36.920
<font color="#00ffff">I am 67, my niece is 20 and healthy</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with it.</font>

35:36.960 --> 35:39.720
<font color="#00ff00">Ah, but remember Princess Charlotte.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">So sad.</font>

35:39.760 --> 35:42.640
<font color="#00ff00">Even healthy women can die in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">childbirth.</font>

35:42.680 --> 35:44.320
<font color="#00ffff">Indeed.</font>

35:44.360 --> 35:46.840
<font color="#00ffff">But I think we must go to Hanover.</font>

35:46.880 --> 35:52.280
<font color="#00ffff">I cannot stand the sight of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">our simpering little Queen a moment</font>
<font color="#00ffff">longer.</font>

35:54.560 --> 35:59.720
<font color="#00ff00">The Rooshian is engaged to someone</font>
<font color="#00ff00">else, Mrs Jenkins, so that's your</font>
<font color="#00ff00">sixpence gone.</font>

35:59.760 --> 36:05.160
<font color="#00ff00">And Georgie Porgie hasn't been near</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the Palace in days, so that's mine</font>
<font color="#00ff00">gone too.</font>

36:06.160 --> 36:08.760
<font color="#00ffff">We had no business gambling on such</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a thing.</font>

36:08.800 --> 36:11.160
<font color="#00ffff">It's the devil's work.</font>

36:11.200 --> 36:14.160
<font color="#ffff00">I don't think the Queen</font>
<font color="#ffff00">is about to marry anyone, Mr Penge.</font>

36:14.880 --> 36:16.920
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps you should all take your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">money back.</font>

36:16.960 --> 36:20.160
<font color="#00ffff">Excuse me,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but Prince Albert's still in the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">running.</font>

36:20.200 --> 36:23.080
<font color="#00ff00">Is he here? If he is, I hadn't</font>
<font color="#00ff00">noticed him.</font>

36:26.920 --> 36:29.040
Some days I really wish I was a man.

36:30.320 --> 36:33.000
They don't spend all day
trussed up like a chicken.

36:33.040 --> 36:35.560
<font color="#00ffff">They have to shave, Ma'am.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">That can't be comfortable.</font>

36:35.600 --> 36:38.880
I'd rather shave than wear one of
these.
(Cannon fires)

36:39.560 --> 36:41.520
Is something the matter, Mrs
Jenkins?

36:41.560 --> 36:44.280
<font color="#00ff00">Why don't you go and lie down, Mrs</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Jenkins.</font>

36:47.360 --> 36:49.360
<font color="#00ffff">May I be excused, Ma'am?</font>

36:49.400 --> 36:50.760
Of course.

37:01.200 --> 37:02.800
Is she unwell?

37:05.200 --> 37:07.200
<font color="#00ff00">It's the Newport Chartists, Ma'am.</font>

37:07.240 --> 37:09.560
<font color="#00ff00">They are to be executed any day now.</font>

37:09.600 --> 37:13.880
<font color="#00ff00">Mrs Jenkins is from those parts.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Well, she takes it hard.</font>

37:18.480 --> 37:20.880
Do many people feel as Mrs Jenkins
does?

37:23.120 --> 37:25.120
<font color="#00ff00">I think they do, Ma'am, yes.</font>

37:25.800 --> 37:28.280
<font color="#00ff00">They may not hold with the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Chartists, but...</font>

37:28.920 --> 37:31.040
<font color="#00ff00">they don't want them to die a</font>
<font color="#00ff00">traitor's death.</font>

37:32.560 --> 37:34.280
No.

37:34.960 --> 37:36.960
No, it's a...

37:37.320 --> 37:39.320
..terrible way to die.

37:44.960 --> 37:46.960
<font color="#ffff00">You sent for me, Ma'am?</font>

37:50.160 --> 37:52.360
When are the Newport Chartists
to be executed?

37:52.400 --> 37:54.280
<font color="#ffff00">Next Friday, Ma'am.</font>

37:54.320 --> 37:59.320
They are to be hanged, drawn and
quartered? <font color="#ffff00">That is the punishment for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">treason, Ma'am.</font>

37:59.360 --> 38:02.920
<font color="#ffff00">I believe some bishops</font>
<font color="#ffff00">are organising a petition for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">clemency.</font>

38:02.960 --> 38:04.520
Then I should like to sign it.

38:05.400 --> 38:07.400
Such a punishment is not civilised.

38:08.800 --> 38:11.800
<font color="#ffff00">I fear you do not understand</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the severity of the crime, Ma'am.</font>

38:11.840 --> 38:15.800
Indeed I do, but I think you do not
understand the severity of the
punishment.

38:15.840 --> 38:18.800
Such things may have been necessary
in the reign of Elizabeth...

38:19.800 --> 38:22.880
..but I would like my reign to be a
merciful one.

38:25.320 --> 38:28.800
<font color="#ffff00">Then you must know, Ma'am, that as</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Queen...</font>

38:30.080 --> 38:31.880
<font color="#ffff00">..you may commute their sentences.</font>

38:32.880 --> 38:37.120
<font color="#ffff00">Instead of being executed,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">they would be transported to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Australia.</font>

38:38.320 --> 38:40.720
In that case, I should like to
exercise my right.

38:41.920 --> 38:43.280
<font color="#ffff00">You are sure, Ma'am?</font>

38:44.560 --> 38:46.040
Quite sure.

38:47.560 --> 38:49.480
(Dash barks)

38:53.600 --> 38:56.560
<font color="#00ff00">I am not sure it's...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Mama. Sir John.</font>

38:56.600 --> 38:58.880
How fortunate to find you here
together.

38:59.480 --> 39:02.240
I have come here
because I wanted to tell you, in
person,

39:02.280 --> 39:05.200
that I have decided
to grant your request, Sir John.

39:06.360 --> 39:09.400
<font color="#00ffff">What request?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Didn't he tell you, Mama?</font>

39:11.360 --> 39:16.280
I am going to give Sir John an Irish
title and a pension of 1,000 a year,

39:16.320 --> 39:18.760
and in return, he is going to leave
Court.

39:21.320 --> 39:23.320
<font color="#00ffff">You would leave me, for...</font>

39:24.160 --> 39:25.520
<font color="#00ffff">..for some money?</font>

39:28.320 --> 39:30.280
You have not changed your mind, Sir
John?

39:33.840 --> 39:35.040
<font color="#00ff00">No.</font>

39:41.000 --> 39:43.440
And I have decided to raise your
allowance, Mama.

39:44.120 --> 39:46.200
It is time you had some new clothes.

39:47.800 --> 39:49.960
Come on, Dash.
(Dash barks)

39:54.720 --> 39:57.240
<font color="#00ff00">You must understand I had no choice.</font>

39:58.600 --> 40:01.080
<font color="#00ff00">I have no desire to leave you.</font>

40:04.160 --> 40:06.280
<font color="#00ff00">But your daughter will not be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">ruled...</font>

40:08.040 --> 40:11.000
<font color="#00ff00">..and I must use my talents</font>
<font color="#00ff00">somewhere.</font>

40:28.920 --> 40:31.440
<font color="#00ff00">SKERRETT:</font>
<font color="#00ff00">The Queen said it wasn't civilised.</font>

40:31.480 --> 40:33.480
<font color="#00ffff">And she's right, God bless her.</font>

40:34.200 --> 40:37.160
<font color="#00ffff">Maybe it takes a Queen to see things</font>
<font color="#00ffff">as they should be.</font>

40:37.880 --> 40:42.480
<font color="#ffff00">I have a letter from my brother in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Dover.</font>

40:42.520 --> 40:44.600
<font color="#ffff00">The Coburg Princes are expected.</font>

40:44.640 --> 40:47.520
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, I am looking forward to my</font>
<font color="#ffff00">winnings.</font>

40:47.560 --> 40:50.280
<font color="#00ff00">I think you are being a bit hasty,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Mr Francatelli.</font>

40:50.920 --> 40:53.200
<font color="#00ff00">There's no guarantee the Queen will</font>
<font color="#00ff00">bite.</font>

40:53.240 --> 40:55.240
<font color="#ffff00">Well, let's wait and see.</font>

40:55.640 --> 40:59.280
<font color="#00ff00">You really think a German sausage</font>
<font color="#00ff00">will tempt our virgin Queen?</font>

40:59.320 --> 41:01.920
<font color="#00ff00">I still think my sixpence is quite</font>
<font color="#00ff00">safe.</font>

41:04.680 --> 41:05.800
Mama?

41:08.320 --> 41:10.560
I have something for you.

41:15.360 --> 41:17.960
The lace is made in a convent in
Bruges.

41:19.360 --> 41:21.160
Look how delicate it is.

41:24.080 --> 41:26.000
<font color="#00ffff">You sent him away, Drina.</font>

41:29.000 --> 41:32.600
No, Mama, he wanted to go.

41:36.320 --> 41:39.840
I know you feel his loss and I
understand.

41:40.960 --> 41:44.320
To lose someone you care for...

41:44.360 --> 41:46.360
It's so hard.

41:52.520 --> 41:54.960
<font color="#00ffff">No man would give you up, Drina...</font>

41:57.040 --> 41:59.760
<font color="#00ffff">..unless he knew that it was his</font>
<font color="#00ffff">duty.</font>

42:03.640 --> 42:05.640
(Tearfully) Oh, Mama...

42:08.440 --> 42:10.440
..I think I will never be happy.

42:10.480 --> 42:12.480
(Sobs) Never.

42:24.000 --> 42:27.760
<font color="#ffff00">Elizabeth seems to have become</font>
<font color="#ffff00">something of a favourite, Ma'am.</font>

42:29.800 --> 42:32.360
I have decided to follow her example
and reign alone.

42:33.960 --> 42:36.440
With companions, perhaps.

42:36.480 --> 42:38.320
<font color="#ffff00">Really, Ma'am?</font>

42:39.920 --> 42:42.920
<font color="#ffff00">Have you told your Coburg cousins?</font>

42:42.960 --> 42:45.960
<font color="#ffff00">I hear the brothers</font>
<font color="#ffff00">have departed for these shores.</font>

42:46.000 --> 42:48.480
Albert and Ernest? But I have not
asked them.

42:48.520 --> 42:51.320
<font color="#ffff00">Nevertheless, they are coming.</font>

42:53.880 --> 42:58.440
Uncle Leopold must have sent for them
against my express instructions.

42:58.480 --> 43:01.520
Why doesn't he understand
I am quite happy as I am?

43:02.800 --> 43:05.520
<font color="#ffff00">I will not be your Prime Minister</font>
<font color="#ffff00">forever, Ma'am.</font>

43:07.920 --> 43:10.680
Don't say that, Lord M.
<font color="#ffff00">But I must.</font>

43:10.720 --> 43:13.200
<font color="#ffff00">Let the Coburgs come.</font>

43:13.960 --> 43:16.400
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps Prince Albert will surprise</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you.</font>

43:22.600 --> 43:23.760
(Sighs)

43:25.320 --> 43:27.320
I don't want things to change.

43:29.400 --> 43:31.400
<font color="#ffff00">I know, Ma'am.</font>

43:32.920 --> 43:35.240
<font color="#ffff00">But I believe you will not be happy</font>
<font color="#ffff00">alone...</font>

43:37.120 --> 43:38.920
<font color="#ffff00">..even with companions.</font>

43:43.120 --> 43:46.720
<font color="#ffff00">You need a husband...to love you...</font>

43:47.360 --> 43:49.160
<font color="#ffff00">..honour you, cherish you.</font>

43:52.040 --> 43:54.080
But there is no-one I care for.

43:57.240 --> 43:59.960
<font color="#ffff00">I do not think you have really</font>
<font color="#ffff00">looked.</font>

44:05.440 --> 44:07.440
I was so happy before.

44:08.160 --> 44:13.320
<font color="#ffff00">I find that happiness can always</font>
<font color="#ffff00">be recollected in tranquillity,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am.</font>

44:14.120 --> 44:16.000
You were happy too?

44:17.040 --> 44:19.040
<font color="#ffff00">You know I was.</font>

44:22.040 --> 44:24.520
Well, I'm not going to get married
just to please you.

44:24.560 --> 44:28.240
<font color="#ffff00">No, you must please yourself.</font>

44:31.440 --> 44:33.440
# Piano Sonata No.15 in F Major

45:42.360 --> 45:43.880
<font color="#00ff00">Victoria.</font>

45:43.920 --> 45:48.360
# Gloriana

45:48.400 --> 45:49.480
Albert?

45:49.520 --> 45:53.000
# Hallelujah...

45:54.120 --> 45:57.200
<font color="#ffff00">It's Albert's destiny to marry</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria.</font>

45:57.520 --> 45:58.960
<font color="#00ffff">I'm not sure Victoria agrees.</font>

45:59.080 --> 46:00.600
Albert and I are not suited.

46:00.640 --> 46:01.920
He has no manners.

46:02.080 --> 46:04.160
<font color="#ffff00">It seemed to me that you play</font>
<font color="#ffff00">together rather well.</font>

46:04.200 --> 46:07.480
<font color="#00ffff">So stiff and awkward.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">A clockwork Prince.</font>

46:08.160 --> 46:09.520
Do you think the Prince handsome?

46:09.560 --> 46:11.600
I would like him to smile at me.

46:12.080 --> 46:16.720
<font color="#ffff00">What's he looking at?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">A woman, or the most eligable match</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in Europe?</font>

46:16.760 --> 46:19.400
I do not need you to tell me what to
think, Albert.

46:19.480 --> 46:22.240
<font color="#00ff00">No. That's </font><font color="#00ff00"> Lord Melbourne's job.</font>

